WEBVTT

00:02.785 --> 00:04.265
- ♪ Hey, here comes Sunny
keeping it fun ♪

00:04.395 --> 00:05.875
♪ Never says never,
never gives up ♪

00:06.006 --> 00:08.443
♪ It's Sunny,
yeah, she's Sunny ♪

00:08.573 --> 00:10.053
♪ Hey

00:10.184 --> 00:11.750
♪ Gear up and go
in the Glam Van ♪

00:11.881 --> 00:13.317
♪ Hair styling
with her best friends ♪

00:13.448 --> 00:16.190
♪ It's Sunny,
yeah, she's Sunny ♪

00:16.320 --> 00:19.280
♪ Oh, it's a Sunny Day

00:19.410 --> 00:21.543
♪ She'll put a smile
on your face ♪

00:21.673 --> 00:23.371
- Whoo-hoo!

00:23.501 --> 00:28.115
- ♪ Sunny is shining
all the way ♪

00:28.245 --> 00:31.118
♪ Yeah, she's Sunny,
yeah, she's Sunny ♪

00:31.248 --> 00:33.468
♪ Having a sunny, sunny day

00:33.598 --> 00:35.122
- Hoo-hoo!

00:40.649 --> 00:42.346
[upbeat music]

00:42.477 --> 00:44.870
- Ugh.

00:45.001 --> 00:48.700
- How's this?
- Mmm, KC wants bigger hair.

00:50.485 --> 00:54.010
- No, this amount of big
is fine, Lacey.

00:54.141 --> 00:56.273
- Bigger.

00:56.404 --> 00:59.363
Bigger!

01:01.496 --> 01:06.240
- Too big, Lacey!
- No problem, let's go smaller.

01:06.370 --> 01:09.112
- What do you think?
- Psh, it was perfect.

01:09.243 --> 01:12.072
Add some pink stripes.
KC loves pink.

01:12.202 --> 01:14.552
And stripes.
- No thanks, really.

01:14.683 --> 01:16.250
- [laughs]
You're so funny, KC.

01:16.380 --> 01:18.078
No, seriously,
she wants pink stripes.

01:18.208 --> 01:20.428
- What I really want
is something simple

01:20.558 --> 01:24.388
for when I play fetch.
- We can do that.

01:24.519 --> 01:28.610
What about poodle puffs?
They're simple and fun.

01:28.740 --> 01:31.178
- Yes!
- Mmm, no.

01:31.308 --> 01:33.267
- But Lacey,
that's what I want.

01:33.397 --> 01:35.095
- That's what
you think you want.

01:35.225 --> 01:38.359
Ooh, you know what I'm seeing?Bows.

01:38.489 --> 01:39.708
- But I want poodle puffs.

01:39.838 --> 01:41.449
- So how many bows
are we thinking?

01:41.579 --> 01:43.755
One big bow,
or lots of little bows?

01:43.886 --> 01:45.670
- [stammering]
But, but, but.

01:45.801 --> 01:47.846
- I'm loving the bow!

01:47.977 --> 01:52.808
- Um, KC, what do you think?
- She loves the bow!

01:52.938 --> 01:54.897
- No, I don't, Lacey.

01:55.027 --> 01:57.073
You never listen
to what I want.

01:57.204 --> 02:00.076
I don't want
big bows or little bows

02:00.207 --> 02:02.774
or pink stripes or fluffy hair.

02:02.905 --> 02:05.995
- Of course I listen.
You said you wanted

02:06.126 --> 02:08.084
big fluffy hair with a bow.

02:08.215 --> 02:10.869
- That's not
what I said at all!

02:11.000 --> 02:13.307
Ugh, that's it, I'm leaving.

02:13.437 --> 02:16.484
Go find a new
best friend to boss around.

02:16.614 --> 02:17.920
Hmph!

02:18.050 --> 02:19.182
- [groans]

02:21.532 --> 02:23.969
- Oh, have a sunny day.

02:24.100 --> 02:25.449
- What did we miss?

02:25.580 --> 02:28.409
[tense music]

02:28.539 --> 02:31.020
♪

02:31.151 --> 02:33.327
- Oh...

02:33.457 --> 02:36.286
[upbeat music]

02:36.417 --> 02:37.983
♪

02:38.114 --> 02:40.290
- Morning, everyone.
both: Good morning.

02:40.421 --> 02:44.251
- Ooh, I can't wait to show you
my latest color collection.

02:44.381 --> 02:46.340
I call it Fairy Brights.

02:46.470 --> 02:49.821
[computer beeping]

02:49.952 --> 02:52.215
all: Lacey?
- Good morning.

02:52.346 --> 02:53.738
- What are you doing here?

02:53.869 --> 02:55.827
- Well, the salon door
was open.

02:55.958 --> 02:57.525
all: What?
- At least it was

02:57.655 --> 02:59.788
after I found your spare key
under the flower pot.

02:59.918 --> 03:02.356
- Great, so what
are you doing here?

03:02.486 --> 03:04.358
- Can't a friend
hang out with other friends

03:04.488 --> 03:07.491
at their salon all day long?
Without warning?

03:07.622 --> 03:10.364
- So, you didn't make up
with KC yesterday, huh?

03:10.494 --> 03:13.410
- Make up with KC?
After she stormed off

03:13.541 --> 03:16.674
and didn't say thank you
for my styling advice?

03:16.805 --> 03:19.155
No way.
When she's ready to say sorry,

03:19.286 --> 03:21.418
she'll find me.
And in the meantime,

03:21.549 --> 03:24.769
I can help around the salon.
- Help around the salon?

03:24.900 --> 03:26.728
[upbeat musical flourish]

03:26.858 --> 03:30.079
- I mean, help around
the salon, yay!

03:30.210 --> 03:32.212
- We'll have
lots of fun, Lacey.

03:32.342 --> 03:34.475
And I'm sure
you'll be a big help.

03:38.522 --> 03:41.569
- Nope, nope, nope.

03:41.699 --> 03:43.048
- Oh, whoa!

03:43.179 --> 03:44.746
- None of these
are fluffy enough.

03:44.876 --> 03:48.793
As I always say to KC,
fluffy hair is awesome hair.

03:48.924 --> 03:51.666
[upbeat musical flourish]

03:51.796 --> 03:54.451
- Those wigs
did need sorting out.

03:56.323 --> 03:57.715
- [laughs]

03:57.846 --> 04:00.544
[computer beeps]

04:00.675 --> 04:02.024
- [gasps]

04:02.154 --> 04:03.895
You know, Lacey,
you don't have to

04:04.026 --> 04:06.898
press all of the buttons
all at the same time.

04:07.029 --> 04:10.598
- Watch and learn, Rox.
[laughs]

04:10.728 --> 04:14.166
[computer whirring]

04:14.297 --> 04:15.429
- Huh?

04:15.559 --> 04:18.388
[whimsical music]

04:18.519 --> 04:23.872
♪

04:24.002 --> 04:26.178
- Red, blue,
yellow, and orange.

04:26.309 --> 04:28.137
If I mix
all the colors together,

04:28.268 --> 04:31.096
we have...

04:31.227 --> 04:34.709
- A muddy brown?
- It's a work in progress.

04:34.839 --> 04:36.450
- You know
what they say, Lacey.

04:36.580 --> 04:39.148
Less is more.
- [laughs]

04:39.279 --> 04:42.238
More is more,
as I always tell KC.

04:42.369 --> 04:44.109
- Oh...

04:44.240 --> 04:47.112
[elegant music]

04:47.243 --> 04:48.331
♪

04:48.462 --> 04:50.377
- Done.
- Hmm.

04:50.507 --> 04:52.553
It's a good try, Blair.

04:52.683 --> 04:54.859
But you should really
sort the nail polishes

04:54.990 --> 04:57.253
by glitter and sparkle factor.

04:57.384 --> 05:00.300
- Making a rainbow
has always worked for me.

05:00.430 --> 05:02.214
- That's because
you didn't know better.

05:02.345 --> 05:05.522
KC always sorts her bows
by how glittery they are.

05:05.653 --> 05:07.132
I taught her that.

05:07.263 --> 05:09.309
Perfect when you need
sparkle in a hurry.

05:09.439 --> 05:11.572
Here, I'll show you.

05:11.702 --> 05:13.878
Oh, now that's glittery.

05:14.009 --> 05:17.229
[sad musical flourish]

05:17.360 --> 05:19.057
- [gasps]

05:19.188 --> 05:22.713
- Oops.
- Thanks.

05:24.236 --> 05:26.282
- Let's get you shampooed.

05:27.936 --> 05:30.982
- Nuh-uh-uh.
Like I tell KC,

05:31.113 --> 05:33.420
you'll never have troubles
with lots of bubbles.

05:33.550 --> 05:35.378
[dramatic musical flourish]

05:35.509 --> 05:37.815
- Ooh.
- Sorry.

05:37.946 --> 05:39.339
- [giggles]

05:39.469 --> 05:42.080
Thanks, Sunny!
- Have a sunny day!

05:42.211 --> 05:43.995
- Sit still, Doodle.

05:44.126 --> 05:45.649
Now where was I?

05:45.780 --> 05:48.043
Ugh, I'll have to start
all over again.

05:48.173 --> 05:51.786
[slowly]
One, two, three.

05:51.916 --> 05:53.483
- Whoa!

05:53.614 --> 05:56.138
- Lacey turned my color chalks
into color soup!

05:56.268 --> 06:00.055
- And who organizes
by sparkles? Who? Who?

06:00.185 --> 06:02.144
- Lacey's only
trying to be helpful.

06:02.274 --> 06:05.756
- All done!
- What's all done?

06:07.062 --> 06:09.281
- Mmm.
- Oh, hi, Sunny.

06:09.412 --> 06:11.936
I thought I'd give Doodle
a special KC makeover.

06:12.067 --> 06:14.374
- Help me!
- Um...

06:14.504 --> 06:16.854
- Oh, I saw some glitter
in the Glam Van

06:16.985 --> 06:19.553
that would be the perfect
finishing touch for Doodle.

06:19.683 --> 06:20.902
I'll go get it.

06:21.032 --> 06:23.905
[tense music]

06:24.035 --> 06:26.821
♪

06:26.951 --> 06:31.521
- Is it just me, or is
everything a little too quiet?

06:31.652 --> 06:35.656
- Yeah.
- Where is Lacey?

06:35.786 --> 06:37.875
all: Ah!
- There you all are.

06:38.006 --> 06:40.704
Good, stay right there.
I'm just going to go get

06:40.835 --> 06:42.967
Blair's sparkles
to go with this glitter.

06:43.098 --> 06:45.709
Because as I say to KC,
if a job's worth doing,

06:45.840 --> 06:49.017
it's worth doing
with glitter and sparkles.

06:49.147 --> 06:50.366
[doorbell jingles]

06:50.497 --> 06:52.499
- Lacey stopped
bossing KC around

06:52.629 --> 06:55.197
and started
bossing us around instead.

06:55.327 --> 06:57.721
- Come on, guys.
Give her a chance.

06:57.852 --> 07:01.203
- Uh, Sunny, I think
you need to see this.

07:03.553 --> 07:05.033
- [gasps]

07:06.556 --> 07:09.385
That's it, we need to get
Lacey and KC back together.

07:09.516 --> 07:12.040
- But how?
- Yeah, KC did seem

07:12.170 --> 07:14.259
pretty angry.
- Just a reminder,

07:14.390 --> 07:16.000
I still have
this bow on my head.

07:16.131 --> 07:18.873
- [laughs]
Oops, sorry, Doodle.

07:19.003 --> 07:20.614
- [barks happily]

07:20.744 --> 07:23.747
- We have to get Lacey
to apologize to KC.

07:23.878 --> 07:25.836
That way, they can
be best friends again.

07:25.967 --> 07:28.448
- Doodle, you lost your bow.

07:28.578 --> 07:30.319
Don't worry,
I'll go get another one.

07:31.625 --> 07:33.148
- We need a plan.

07:33.278 --> 07:36.151
- I'll track down KC.
- And we'll stay here

07:36.281 --> 07:38.893
and keep an eye on Lacey.
- Before she turns it

07:39.023 --> 07:41.852
into Lacey's salon.
- Sorry, Doodle.

07:41.983 --> 07:44.986
You're out of luck.
The only one left was KC's bow,

07:45.116 --> 07:46.596
and she'll be
wanting that back.

07:46.727 --> 07:48.946
But I can give you
a sparkly pedicure.

07:49.077 --> 07:52.123
- Anything but the sparkles!
- I'll hurry.

07:52.254 --> 07:53.995
[adventurous music]

07:54.125 --> 07:57.259
KC, here I come!
- Wait, Doodle, come back here!

07:58.913 --> 08:01.916
- KC, KC.

08:02.046 --> 08:05.441
KC?
- Whoa!

08:05.572 --> 08:07.791
Uh-oh.

08:07.922 --> 08:09.314
- Whoa.

08:10.925 --> 08:14.319
- Hi, Rox.
- What happened here, Cindy?

08:14.450 --> 08:16.626
- Um, it's a little
hard to explain.

08:16.757 --> 08:21.065
I've got a visitor.
- Me! [barks]

08:21.196 --> 08:23.546
- KC, what are you doing
at the bakery?

08:23.677 --> 08:25.243
- This is where I live now!

08:25.374 --> 08:28.029
- Uh, until you
make up with Lacey.

08:28.159 --> 08:31.249
- And have big, fluffy hair
with bows on top?

08:31.380 --> 08:33.338
Hah, no way.

08:33.469 --> 08:35.558
I've been helping Cindy
by coming up

08:35.689 --> 08:37.778
with new ideas for her baking.

08:37.908 --> 08:39.736
Can you believe
she's never made

08:39.867 --> 08:42.217
a fish and blueberry muffin?

08:42.347 --> 08:44.132
- Yes?

08:44.262 --> 08:47.222
- Anyway, Cindy's
my new best friend.

08:47.352 --> 08:50.312
She listens to me,
not like Lacey.

08:50.442 --> 08:53.315
- I'm sure Lacey's missing you.

08:53.445 --> 08:55.709
- Really?
- Really.

08:55.839 --> 08:58.712
- Then why didn't she
come look for me herself?

08:58.842 --> 09:01.497
No, Lacey and I are over.

09:01.628 --> 09:03.717
- Oh...

09:03.847 --> 09:05.719
- [grunting]

09:05.849 --> 09:09.026
- What's she doing?
- Tidying?

09:10.854 --> 09:13.117
- Lacey, thought you
might like a smoothie

09:13.248 --> 09:16.860
after all your hard work.
- Yes, I have worked very hard.

09:16.991 --> 09:18.209
Thanks, Sunny.

09:18.340 --> 09:20.385
I've been organizing
the Glam Van.

09:20.516 --> 09:23.824
It's much better now.
- Yeah, thanks.

09:23.954 --> 09:26.261
Um, Lacey?

09:26.391 --> 09:28.263
Don't you miss KC?

09:28.393 --> 09:29.656
[slurps]

09:29.786 --> 09:35.575
- Miss KC? No way.
Psh, KC who?

09:35.705 --> 09:38.795
- I know how much I'd miss
Blair or Rox or Doodle

09:38.926 --> 09:40.928
if we weren't friends.
- Uh-huh.

09:41.058 --> 09:43.974
Sometimes, I even miss Sunny
when she goes upstairs.

09:44.105 --> 09:45.976
- Well, I don't miss KC.

09:46.107 --> 09:47.717
Just because
we were best friends,

09:47.848 --> 09:49.893
and did everything together,
doesn't mean that I--

09:50.024 --> 09:52.853
- Oh, Sunny, I want
my best friend back!

09:52.983 --> 09:56.334
- Aww, you just need
to talk to KC.

09:56.465 --> 10:00.034
- Wait, you mean talking works?

10:00.164 --> 10:02.645
- Only if you tell her
how you really feel.

10:02.776 --> 10:05.517
But you have to listen as well.

10:05.648 --> 10:08.912
- I suppose I could do that.

10:09.043 --> 10:10.740
But I don't even
know where she is.

10:10.871 --> 10:12.916
- KC is at
the bakery with Cindy!

10:13.047 --> 10:14.831
[exhales]

10:14.962 --> 10:18.705
- Come on, let's go get
your best friend back, Lacey.

10:18.835 --> 10:23.579
Ready, set.
all: Gear up and go!

10:23.710 --> 10:26.364
- Yeah, about that.

10:26.495 --> 10:30.760
Why don't we go with,
one, two, three, come with me!

10:30.891 --> 10:33.023
- We can talk about it
on the way.

10:33.154 --> 10:34.982
[upbeat music]

10:35.112 --> 10:37.593
- Bye, good luck!

10:39.682 --> 10:42.163
- Hi, Cindy.
- Hi, everyone.

10:42.293 --> 10:44.078
Have you come for KC?

10:44.208 --> 10:47.603
You have come
for KC, haven't you?

10:47.734 --> 10:49.779
- Hello, Lacey.

10:49.910 --> 10:51.825
- Hello, KC.

10:51.955 --> 10:54.349
[tense music]

10:54.479 --> 10:56.656
I'm waiting.
- What for?

10:56.786 --> 10:59.267
- Your apology.
- My apology?

10:59.397 --> 11:01.312
I'm waiting for your apology.

11:01.443 --> 11:03.271
You're the one
who didn't listen to me.

11:03.401 --> 11:05.882
- And you're the one
who stormed out of the salon!

11:06.013 --> 11:08.058
- Please be friends!

11:08.189 --> 11:11.714
Best friends are the best,
so you should listen to them

11:11.845 --> 11:15.718
and not boss them around.
- Or put bows on them.

11:15.849 --> 11:20.027
- Oh, that reminds me,
I brought your bow for you, KC.

11:20.157 --> 11:21.681
See what a good friend I am?

11:21.811 --> 11:24.292
There, that's better.

11:24.422 --> 11:26.555
- You haven't listened,
and you're not sorry,

11:26.686 --> 11:29.732
and I am out of here!
[grunts]

11:29.863 --> 11:32.474
[dramatic musical flourish]

11:33.823 --> 11:36.217
- That didn't
go very well, did it?

11:36.347 --> 11:39.263
- I think she was
really missing you, Lacey.

11:39.394 --> 11:41.744
Right until
she stormed out, I mean.

11:41.875 --> 11:45.661
- Let's go after her.
- Mmm, fish and blueberry.

11:45.792 --> 11:47.228
Yum!

11:47.358 --> 11:50.013
Would you like me
to clean this mess up, Cindy?

11:50.144 --> 11:52.712
- [laughs]
They're all yours, Doodle.

11:52.842 --> 11:54.757
Enjoy.
- Come on.

11:54.888 --> 11:57.325
Bye, Cindy.
- Bye-bye!

12:10.120 --> 12:14.734
- Guess I'm just a dog who's
all alone in the world now.

12:14.864 --> 12:17.693
[tense music]

12:17.824 --> 12:18.955
♪

12:19.086 --> 12:20.174
- [gasps]
What's this?

12:20.304 --> 12:23.046
A stray pooch with no owner?

12:23.177 --> 12:26.615
Hey, wait,
isn't Lacey your owner?

12:26.746 --> 12:29.531
- Used to be.
She also used to be

12:29.661 --> 12:33.840
my best friend, but now
I'm a no-best-friend dog.

12:33.970 --> 12:37.234
[crying]
It's a very sad story.

12:37.365 --> 12:40.107
- Well, it's my job
to take care of stray dogs.

12:40.237 --> 12:43.632
So you'd better
come with me to the pound.

12:43.763 --> 12:45.590
- [barks nervously]

12:48.550 --> 12:49.812
[panting]

12:49.943 --> 12:53.033
So are you going
to be my best friend now?

12:53.163 --> 12:57.080
- Um, no?
- You'll come around!

12:59.430 --> 13:02.129
- [gasps]
KC!

13:02.259 --> 13:04.653
- ♪ The wheels on this truck
go round and round ♪

13:04.784 --> 13:07.134
♪ round and round
- She didn't hear me.

13:07.264 --> 13:11.138
Just like all those times
I didn't listen to KC.

13:11.268 --> 13:12.617
And now it's too late.

13:12.748 --> 13:15.055
KC's gone,
and it's all my fault.

13:15.185 --> 13:17.666
I'll never see
my best friend again.

13:17.797 --> 13:21.235
[long]
Never!

13:21.365 --> 13:23.454
- Never say never, Lacey.

13:23.585 --> 13:25.935
- You're right, Sunny.
I'll never give up on KC.

13:26.066 --> 13:27.328
Follow that truck!

13:27.458 --> 13:29.591
- I've got a pretty good idea

13:29.721 --> 13:32.246
where Scratch
might have taken her.

13:32.376 --> 13:35.162
[playful music]

13:35.292 --> 13:39.253
♪

13:39.383 --> 13:41.777
- Right, then.
Sleep tight.

13:41.908 --> 13:45.215
- Hey, aren't you
going to tuck me in?

13:45.346 --> 13:49.089
- [exhales]

13:49.219 --> 13:53.093
- And teddy, Lacey always
tucked my teddy in, too.

13:53.223 --> 13:54.746
- Ugh.

13:57.488 --> 14:00.752
- And tell me a story?
- I don't know any stories.

14:00.883 --> 14:03.451
- [laughs]
You haven't had much practice

14:03.581 --> 14:05.845
with this
best friend thing, have you?

14:09.500 --> 14:12.677
- Okay, KC, um...

14:12.808 --> 14:17.595
Once upon a time, there was
a dog called, uh, Macy.

14:17.726 --> 14:21.164
And she went
to sleep right away.

14:21.295 --> 14:23.253
Which meant she got a
doggie biscuit in the morning.

14:23.384 --> 14:25.690
The end.
- One doggie biscuit?

14:25.821 --> 14:28.302
- [exhales]
- Step aside, Scratch.

14:28.432 --> 14:30.434
I'm here for my best friend,

14:30.565 --> 14:32.610
and I'm not
leaving without her.

14:32.741 --> 14:35.352
- Scratch is my
best friend now.

14:35.483 --> 14:38.138
- [gasps]
- We barely know each other.

14:38.268 --> 14:40.836
- And he's bringing me
lots of biscuits!

14:40.967 --> 14:43.708
- One biscuit.
- You're too late, Lacey.

14:43.839 --> 14:45.362
I've moved on.

14:45.493 --> 14:48.365
- I know I haven't been
a very good friend, KC.

14:48.496 --> 14:51.020
And I'm sorry I haven't
always listened to you.

14:51.151 --> 14:52.892
I just hope
your new best friend

14:53.022 --> 14:55.111
realizes how lucky he is.

14:55.242 --> 14:59.028
- Lacey, do you know what KC's
favorite doggie biscuit is?

14:59.159 --> 15:02.858
- Fish and blueberries.
- [gasps], that's true.

15:02.989 --> 15:05.469
- And what about
KC's favorite color?

15:05.600 --> 15:08.037
- KC has no favorite color.

15:08.168 --> 15:10.910
- It wouldn't be fair
to all the other colors.

15:11.040 --> 15:13.347
- You know, it sounds to me

15:13.477 --> 15:16.306
like this is
a friendship worth saving.

15:16.437 --> 15:19.266
[inspiring music]

15:19.396 --> 15:23.705
- ♪ If you need someone
that is easy to talk to ♪

15:23.835 --> 15:27.578
♪ With them
the sky's always blue ♪

15:27.709 --> 15:30.755
♪ Oh, and if
they make you smile ♪

15:30.886 --> 15:32.975
- ♪ And if you
like their style ♪

15:33.106 --> 15:36.587
both: ♪ And hey if they
